	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Also MMC5 as I recall has no fixed bank. Also when doing MMC5 PRG switching remember there is a PRG-RAM and PRG-ROM involved. I believe bit 7 has to be set to point to ROM rather than PRG-RAM for the area 8000$ to $DFFF. $6000 is always RAM and $E000 is always ROM I think.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


